    IndividualMessageService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for managing individual messages, including retrieving individual messages between users and filtered messages.

    InterestService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for managing interests, including adding, retrieving, and removing interests.

    KeywordService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for managing keywords, including adding, retrieving, and removing keywords.

    MembershipService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for managing project memberships, including adding, removing, and retrieving members.

    NotificationService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for managing notifications, including retrieving unread notifications and marking notifications as read.
    ProjectService
    ProjectService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for managing projects, including creation, retrieval, updating, and approval of projects.
    ReportService
    ReportService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for generating and retrieving project and asset reports in both JSON and PDF formats.
    SkillService
    SkillService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for skill management, including adding, retrieving, and removing skills for users and projects.

    TaskService is a JAX-RS resource class that provides RESTful endpoints for task management, including task creation, updates, dependencies, and retrievals by project.
    UserService
